.000Z","msg":"套漫畫影響對我幾大....<br />\n搞到我中學好想有個穩定拍長拖女朋友..<br />\n同埋鐘意阿圓果種姐姐型壞女仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SkKyeoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkKyeoW.jpg&h=c8873b75&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"阿圓是完美<br />\n以阿圓作為標準<br />\n會搞到搵唔到女朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd6e028a0799354d3bf74bf2ccadb6af181510a","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"Wiki 鮎川圓<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AE%8E%E5%B7%9D%E5%9C%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AE%258E%25E5%25B7%259D%25E5%259C%2593&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=5e99e7b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AE%8E%E5%B7%9D%E5%9C%93</a><br />\n<br />\n原作者松本泉曾表示（愛藏版第3卷）｢鮎川圓」的名字是來自SHEENA &amp; THE ROKKETS的「鮎川誠」和ダディ竹千代&amp;東京おとぼけCATS（Daddy竹千代&amp;東京裝傻CATS）的主唱「さんままどか」，鮎川圓的原型則是來自發行專輯「少女A」時期的中森明菜。"},{"pid":"c27bf856fea53b00bbfa862021eb93323a0e999c","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"但願回到過去（あの日にかえりたい） ending<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZIOtIpWWDDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZIOtIpWWDDg&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=aa672ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZIOtIpWWDDg</a>"},{"pid":"2abf0a65451045216c3b2ed224040b4ccbf0d46c","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:53:55.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A9%2599%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=6c24f0aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n對於這個角色設定，松本泉曾在漫畫版序裡面提及，本來是希望鮎川圓交過很多男朋友且也已經不是處女，但後來受到漫畫迷的抗議而把她設定成從未交過男朋友。"},{"pid":"5c971e0c57d502be291b50dff5ee011736f0e39d","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=60037&amp;snB=929322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D60037%26snB%3D929322&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=4ffed7ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=60037&amp;snB=929322</a><br />\n<br />\n阿圓的造型設定藍本是來自80年代當紅的偶像中森明菜與川島直美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iXZVkbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiXZVkbO.jpg&h=066d5813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hl42z7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHl42z7Z.jpg&h=745acd08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"003f3d8dd848a40ca1bbd4a005a33fb3ff79f144","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<a href=\"https://ptt.jimpop.org/c30058554b55\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fptt.jimpop.org%2Fc30058554b55&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=a5e871df\" target=\"_blank\">https://ptt.jimpop.org/c30058554b55</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zOirecG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzOirecG.jpg&h=5a6fc6c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f94d001f7c49fd2cebeff3dad80c6be7e6aea","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:46:51.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<a href=\"https://k22k5566.pixnet.net/blog/post/159750905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fk22k55