えりたい） ending<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZIOtIpWWDDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZIOtIpWWDDg&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=aa672ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZIOtIpWWDDg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:54:36.000Z","msg":"失戀神歌"},{"pid":"5de09dddd716c5cbb58c7358dfbac4dec0aefba4","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1440079d715037ad655c285ed9ccd4e95fca9aba","tid":1959991,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"想回到那一天當年喊到Fe le fat lat<br />\n不過松本泉話唔係好鍾意呢套嘢<br />\n太傷感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"覺得呢個結局好過漫畫嗰個結局<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 好奇想知道，有冇source，松本泉喺邊度講過唔鍾意？thx."},{"pid":"5d8f8b57f4cc1d18bb303cdeb7260b3d41e74a32","tid":1959991,"uid":131437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A9%2599%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=b87a7f56\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者松本泉在連載期間就常因為健康狀況不良，而導致後來的長期休載。休載前和再連載後的一段時間，因為畫風差異很大，讀者便猜測是由萩原一至（日語：萩原一至）代筆。事實上只有在松本無法執筆暫時由萩原代畫，在連載完結前萩原就離開了工作室，松本也在官方的Fanbook裏否定這項流言。另外長期讓松本困擾的症狀在2004年查明是腦髓液減少症（日語：脳脊髄液減少症）。<br />\n<br />\n單行本化時就有相當多修改，特別是最後一集修改幅度最大。愛藏版發行時也經過了修改，所以連載版、JC（Jump Comics）版和愛藏版的最終回是完全不一樣的。"},{"pid":"514e0d5b8e860a99999c95913c968a23ec956982","tid":1959991,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}